msgstr ""

msgctxt "Feature/&PowerPactChainPseudodragonDescription"
msgid ""
"Binds a Pseudodragon to your warlock, granting advantage on saving throws "
"against spells and other magical effects."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Feature/&PowerPactChainQuasitTitle"
