msgstr ""

msgctxt "Feature/&FeatureSetPactBladeDescription"
msgid ""
"The warlock becomes proficient with Martial weapons and imbues weapons with "
"the capacity to overcome resistance or immunity to damage from non-magical "
"weapons"
msgstr ""

