msgctxt "Feature/&PowerPatronFiendDarkOnesBlessingTitle"
msgid "Dark One's Blessing"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Feature/&PowerPatronFiendDarkOnesBlessingDescription"
msgid ""
"Starting at 1st level, when you reduce a hostile creature to 0 hit points, "
"you gain temporary hit points equal to your Charisma modifier + your warlock "
"level (minimum of 1)."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Feature/&PowerPatronFiendDarkOnesOwnLuckTitle"
msgid "Dark One's Own Luck"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Feature/&PowerPatronFiendDarkOnesOwnLuckDescription"
msgid ""
"You can use an action to bring forth a fiendish stroke of luck. For the next "
"minute, you roll an additional 1d10 on all your ability checks and saving "
"throws. Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a "
"long rest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Feature/&FeatureSetPatronFiendFiendishResilienceTitle"
msgid "Fiendish Resilience"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Feature/&FeatureSetPatronFiendFiendishResilienceDescription"
msgid ""
"Starting at the 10th level, you can choose one damage type when you finish a "
"short or long rest. You gain resistance to that damage type until you choose "
"a different one with this feature. Damage from magical weapons or silver "
"weapons ignores this resistance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Feature/&PowerFiendishResilienceDescription"
msgid ""
"Gain resistance to this type of damage, except for weapons which are magical "
"or made of silver."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Feature/&PowerFiendishResilienceAcidTitle"
msgid "Fiendish Resilience (Acid)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Feature/&PowerFiendishResilienceBludgeoningTitle"
