msgctxt "Feature/&PowerBardHeroismBolsterMoraleTitle"
msgid "Bolster Morale"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Feature/&PowerBardHeroismBolsterMoraleDescription"
msgid ""
"When an ally uses one of your Bardic Inspiration dice, they roll twice and "
